{"tid":1296913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當義士俾幾隻狗捉住，我諗到個方法解救","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:10:19.000Z","uid":276426,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba8c72a22989eb4d57fac45f90094595cb97ec3","tid":1296913,"uid":276426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"參考隔離post問 狗最怕咩，最多人答係 有錢佬 鬼佬 ，綜合黎講 狗怕 權貴。<br />\n所以當有義士俾幾隻狗捉住，旁邊的人可以大叫 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你做咩打 駐日大使個囝/囡， </span></span> ，or 其他國家啦(不過亞洲國家會似d，因為義士係亞洲人樣）。 班狗會縮一縮，義士就趁機走！<br />\n<br />\n當然義士不是冒充，只是旁邊的人認錯人。<br />\n<br />\n此方法只是緩兵之計，救人要快手！<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗？ 集思廣益"},{"pid":"13e594c6f48dd789eb68ac49d3e01bf9a6bbb317","tid":1296913,"uid":276426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"986e3105332cdadb1e300ac8fd80d4960c832f1d","tid":1296913,"uid":276426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e2107307babe2dcbff1447260abbf532d75c30d","tid":1296913,"uid":276426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4f9d6b4ce9b63534bda09a25efa792315c86a0c6","tid":1296913,"uid":22465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"老實講，好幼稚"},{"pid":"6de781b635580394bc67172d5e4cc046f544269b","tid":1296913,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f9d6b4ce9b63534bda09a25efa792315c86a0c6","tid":1296913,"uid":22465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"老實講，好幼稚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"係 同埋都無可能<br />\n班死差佬連字都唔識多隻<br />\n理撚得你係邊 打撚左先算"},{"pid":"2768c8453d5ca38c4a4b26fcbb2c7558ea111671","tid":1296913,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會信架，襯班狗聚埋黎前救最實際<br />\n但個一𣊬間要刻服好多野"},{"pid":"daee460f24afaf02